data.description: PERFECT STARTER HOME OR RETIREE HAVEN! This neat, clean and move-in ready 2/2 is centrally located to all the conveniences of Sebring. The great split plan features a galley kitchen with eat-at bar and cozy breakfast nook. Master bedroom includes a large walk-in closet and en suite bath with step-in shower. You'll love the relaxing lanai overlooking a peaceful pond and state-owned land for privacy that won't ever be disturbed! Make your appointment to view this one quick before it's gone!
